{"tid":1793554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"城門河單嘢都有被自殺嘅可能","createTime":"2019-12-22T13:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:17:11.000Z","uid":200636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9db81f813fb4ef7c3b131cc028609e42dce172","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:05:35.000Z","msg":"請大家細閱此文，尤其係第一個受害個案<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochweekly.com/b5/125/6485.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochweekly.com%2Fb5%2F125%2F6485.htm&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=1ddeba32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochweekly.com/b5/125/6485.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係發生過係自己屋企身上，我都會好懷疑迷魂煙呢樣嘢，但第一個個案正正同我屋企人經歷的有9成相似，所以，當我今日睇到城門河單嘢，我第一時間覺得，死者會唔會中咗迷魂煙而做出一啲難以理解嘅行為<br />\n<br />\n可能之前太多被自殺案都太求其，而且又無目擊証人之下，就宣判死因無可疑，但今次我係facebook度睇到，好似有一位巿民親眼睇住死者自己跳河，相信大家覺得好匪夷所思，甚至開始懷疑之前的所謂被自殺，我希望大家真係真係唔好覺得手足會咁樣自殺，點解要封住個口，係因為手足怕自己會掙扎求存而咁做？咁點解唔揀跳樓？唔通咁死自己會舒服啲？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;迷魂煙&ldquo;係可以解通呢啲疑團，它能夠控制一個人嘅意識行為，再離譜嘅都有可能，大家諗下，會唔會係有人想將死者嘅行為被目擊到，而釋除一啲被自殺嘅講法呢？<br />\n<br />\n我文筆唔好，未必所有人能明白我想表達嘅嘢，我只希望大家上網了解下關於&ldquo;迷魂煙&ldquo;，雖然資訊亦唔太多，但絕對似中共用開嘅手法<br />\n<br />\n最後，我唔知出完呢個post之後，會唔會有人話我啲乜，總之，我只係想比多個方向大家思考下，唔想有任何手足枉死<br />\n<br />\n另本人熱愛生命，亦非常怕死，所以絕不自殺"},{"pid":"12e1f9dffe83330a4f4f974b1fc51ab502e8cb64","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"c14a05d6b20ec3453f5b36e32c95fe74ccb48f14","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"02c12dcdb10b75909cb423f526fb919c03414df4","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:06:44.000Z","msg":"人"},{"pid":"b9c7303da95f2b3690b2cfcefe919aa8522c27bd","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"報"},{"pid":"6b4f8d7ffff83b305644941a43b93e2b5193d3d3","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"仇"},{"pid":"9cec52e994b8491d1654aebafe7d31afff74e9a0","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:07:18.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"490dd298276e25682dbd971b4101bf358d6dccfa","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"363b54c1fe6733b4c7432c37be4879075c9e01a1","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:07:40.000Z","msg":"人"},{"pid":"f9a003e9073cbca141adb148413d69f5eddf8f9d","tid":1793554,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:07:46.000Z","msg":"邊有人自殺會喺個口痴膠帶"},{"pid":"4da916122f1c38e81eeee9b8e5f46ee2a733beda","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"反"},{"pid":"d543935adc2a081820316a7a5a584e3174f6772b","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T13:08:04.000Z","msg":"抗"},{"pid":"0ff77316807d58bb05010818e5f740cec0e25a4b","tid":1793554,"uid":200636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T14:01:18.000Z","msg":"人言微輕"},{"pid":"89fe4a2bf97458dcaa92729098f368e55b1f9c8f","tid":1793554,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}